{"tid":1101914,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"唱左幾十年k，分享下和階唱k攻略","createTime":"2019-04-11T10:43:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-12T13:18:39.000Z","uid":107157,"like":13,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4812e495e3e8ca1887631ecb750e235d85e0bd17","tid":1101914,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T10:43:24.000Z","msg":"頭先見隔離post 講唱k啲黑人憎既野，相信大家都遇過，唱左幾十年k既我都有唔少感受，所以同大家分享下心得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先講下最大果4個問題先<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">NG行為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:</span></span><br />\n1. 疊聲<br />\n疊聲可以引起好多問題，例如鬥大聲，冇得聽自己唱成點，被人影響等等。所以主力都係要解決呢個問題。<br />\n<br />\n2. 一次過點滿成版歌/好多歌<br />\n呢種行為會搞到自己想唱既歌冇得唱，就算random播都阻止唔到。結果去唱k變左去白坐。<br />\n<br />\n3. 人地唱歌時你大聲同其他人講閒野<br />\n超級唔尊重人，好似當人冇到，仲會搞到唱歌條友好老尷，覺得係咪唱得好難聽唔想聽。最後，一係就火撚滾唔唱，一係就屌鳩你。<br />\n<br />\n4. 咪霸<br />\n成日拎撚住支咪唔放，人地問到仲搶其他人支咪比人，唔比自己咪人。搞到神憎鬼厭。<br />\n<br />\n一個良好既唱k環境其實需要大家互相既合作同了解，咁樣包你每次唱k都會唱到你高潮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">和平篇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n呢幾個係我平時既解決方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:<br />\n<br />\n1. 疊聲<br />\n其實可以跟首歌而每人唱一個chorus同verse, 到後面剩低既先大合唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 一次過點滿成版歌/好多歌<br />\n其實每次點1，2首歌就夠，點太多人地隨時唔gur你會del你歌，會產生惡性循環。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 唱歌時其他人講野<br />\n其實想講野果時，不妨可以係首歌唔洗唱既地方先講野啦，咁樣唱果個又可以參與到討論，又可以尊重到人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 咪霸<br />\n其實想杜絕呢種情況好簡單，每次唱k剩係約4個以內既人去唱就搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果4個人以上，可以試下大家唱完放支咪上枱，要唱自己拎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">戰爭篇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n有啲人相處唔落，又唔肯合作，就要用呢啲招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 疊聲<br />\n通常疊聲既人唱歌都好撚難聽，哎歌多過唱歌，所以先要搵你做遮掩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係佢唱得好陶醉時，係呢個時候偷偷地轉做純音樂，然後你突然唔唱，個仆街仔就會現形，到時等比人笑柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 一次過點好多歌<br />\n對付呢種人最緊要夠陰濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當佢點到成版歌時，你要做簡歌既背後操控者。首先，同佢講用random播歌，然後每次都係首歌既結尾插播你既歌，然後偷偷取消random，直到你首歌播果陣就轉返random。等條傻鳩仲以為自己好撚醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 唱歌時其他人講野<br />\n對付呢種人要採取強硬手斷。當你唱歌有人講野時，你即刻大聲鳩唱歌，務求聲音要蓋過佢地講野既聲音，再唔夠就將支咪教到最大聲，嘈到佢地講唔到野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 咪霸<br />\n呢種仆街最好對付，只要活用上面3種NG行為對付佢，條仆街會即刻冇晒mood唱k，最後敗走。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實唱k都係想開心姐，大家互相體諒下，人人有k唱，活動先會長久。諗下你咁大個人，唱k時可以玩到幾癲幾開心，以後朋友有各自生活，幾可再有人陪你唱k,仲唱埋通宵k<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9d29738750671a382d6ac0e3e22311b62f415e9","tid":1101914,"uid":176802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T10:45:16.000Z","msg":"咩係和階"},{"pid":"5615af9c401f64b39779db5dcb4c581b415b8a04","tid":1101914,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d9d29738750671a382d6ac0e3e22311b62f415e9","tid":1101914,"uid":176802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T10:45:16.000Z","msg":"咩係和階"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T10:54:51.000Z","msg":"打錯字<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n手機速成個表成日轉 禁錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18f17f1636ed7aab54617907a993a1c680f05663","tid":1101914,"uid":120892,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T11:00:01.000Z","msg":"仲以為你會話唱K有d咩歌唱技巧...."},{"pid":"8fe30e7ca7b435856338e6fd99d3d8d0bff5b7b9","tid":1101914,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T11:00:01.000Z","msg":"高質post冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0abc142c20d4a68f69c82a2168510973b56ea40d","tid":1101914,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"18f17f1636ed7aab54617907a993a1c680f05663","tid":1101914,"uid":120892,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T11:00:01.000Z","msg":"仲以為你會話唱K有d咩歌唱技巧...."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T11:00:34.000Z","msg":"你教我就差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c6ad48e313e436211f077e04a5fbb92fbc894ca","tid":1101914,"uid":120892,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T11:01:25.000Z","msg":"問吓樓主，<br />\n同第一次見面嘅人唱K好老尷<br />\n習慣開伴唱否則唱唔到又點搞？"},{"pid":"954f98566036b6e6b3f07eb6ea90d554326c67b8","tid":1101914,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T11:03:04.000Z","msg":"too long"},{"pid":"71d84edfd65ccd0924523c0fb358eb8e9e1c9b8f","tid":1101914,"uid":201632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T11:03:55.000Z","msg":"唱高音走音點化解尷尬？"},{"pid":"8bde0aa259585431604a642c2bba72e33ccdc9d2","tid":1101914,"uid":200834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T11:06:31.000Z","msg":"朋友唔肯俾我降key點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"003f627c2158632417007a4c3c6198b42eefacca","tid":1101914,"uid":107157,"like":1,"disli